OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,FPlumber, plasterer and now
OL,7,Fparliamentarian.
OL,9,FThe Green Party's Hannah Spencer has
OL,10,Fsecured an historic by-election
OL,11,Fvictory in Gorton and Denton - making
OL,12,Fher the North West's first MP, and
OL,13,Ftheir first by-election win.
OL,15,FThe 34-year-old overturned a
OL,16,Fsignificant Labour majority in the
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Consistency and
OL,18,Frelegated Sir Keir Starmer's party to
OL,19,Fthird place, behind Reform UK's Matt
OL,20,FGoodwin.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
