OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,FThe new MP, who was the leader of the
OL,7,FGreen Party group on Trafford Council,
OL,8,Fclinched the seat with 14,980 votes `
OL,9,Fa majority of 4,402.
OL,11,FWho is the new Gorton and Denton MP
OL,12,Fand where is she from?
OL,14,FHannah, who previously lived in
OL,15,FGorton, left education at 16 before
OL,16,Fgoing on to work as a plumber.
OL,18,FShe set up her own business in January
OL,19,F2015 and worked for other companies,
OL,20,Fplumbing homes around the region and
OL,21,Fworking as a specialist in heat pumps.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
