OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,FDespite her career as a skilled
OL,7,Ftradesperson, the new MP is not new to
OL,8,Fpolitics; she was first elected onto
OL,9,FTrafford council in May 2023,
OL,10,Frepresenting the Hale ward.
OL,12,FWithin a year, she ran against Andy
OL,13,FBurnham and four other candidates for
OL,14,Fthe role of Greater Manchester mayor,
OL,15,Ffinishing fifth - an increased vote
OL,16,Fshare for the Greens over their 2021
OL,17,Fresult.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
