PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772212805
OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,FAway from work and politics, Hannah
OL,7,Fspends free time with her four
OL,8,Fgreyhounds - Olive, Judy, Forest and
OL,9,FWill.
OL,11,FIn February 2026, Hannah was elected
OL,12,Fas the new Gorton and Denton MP, the
OL,13,FGreen Party's fifth MP, and first in
OL,14,FGreater Manchester.
OL,16,FHow many votes did Hannah Spencer win
OL,17,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election by?
OL,19,FThe turnout in the Gorton and Denton
OL,20,Fby-election was 47.62%, with 36,903
OL,21,Fverified votes cast.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
