OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,FHannah Spencer emerged victorious for
OL,7,Fthe Greens, with 14,980 votes and a
OL,8,Fmajority of 4,402 votes.
OL,10,FReform UK's candidate Matt Goodwin got
OL,11,F10,578 votes, with Labour's Angeliki
OL,12,FStogia trailing on 9,364, down from
OL,13,F18,555 in the 2024 general election,
OL,14,Fwhen the turnout was similarly high.
OL,16,FConservative candidate Charlotte
OL,17,FCadden received just 706 votes, with
OL,18,Fthe Liberal Democrats getting 653.
OL,20,FOther candidates secured the following
OL,21,Fvotes:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
