OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,FWhat did Hannah Spencer promise in her
OL,7,Fvictory speech?
OL,9,FWhen Hannah Spencer claimed victory in
OL,10,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election, she
OL,11,Fsaid in a speech: "I didn't grow up
OL,12,Fwanting to be a politician. I am a
OL,13,Fplumber.
OL,15,F"I am no different to every single
OL,16,Fperson here in this constituency. I
OL,17,Fwork hard. That is what we do. Except
OL,18,Fthings have changed a lot over the
OL,19,Flast few decades, because working hard
OL,20,Fused to get me something.
OL,26,@sD@SOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772212805
OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,F"It got you a house, a nice life,
OL,7,Fholidays, it got you somewhere. But
OL,8,Fnow, working hard, what does that get
OL,9,Fyou?"
OL,11,F"Because life has changed. Instead of
OL,12,Fworking for a nice life, we're working
OL,13,Fto line the pockets of billionaires.
OL,14,FWe are being bled dry.
OL,16,F"People in their thousands told me, on
OL,17,Fthe doorstep and at the ballot box,
OL,18,Fthat what we are sick of is being let
OL,19,Fdown and looked down on.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772212805
OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,FShe added: "I won't accept this
OL,7,Fvictory tonight without calling out
OL,8,Fpoliticians and divisive figures who
OL,9,Fconstantly scapegoat and blame our
OL,10,Fcommunities for all the problems in
OL,11,Fsociety.
OL,13,F"My Muslim friends and neighbours are
OL,14,Fjust like me, human.
OL,16,F"Now, to my customers, I'm sorry, but
OL,17,FI think I might have to cancel the
OL,18,Fwork that you haven't booked in,
OL,19,Fbecause I'm heading to Parliament.
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772212805
OL,3,CWho is the Gorton and Denton's new
OL,4,CGreen party Hannah Spencer?
OL,6,F"And when I get there, I will make
OL,7,Fspace for everyone doing jobs like
OL,8,Fmine. We will finally get a seat at
OL,9,Fthe table.
OL,11,F"We can demand better without hating
OL,12,Feach other. We ran a hopeful campaign
OL,13,Fbacked by thousands of volunteers and
OL,14,Factivists.
OL,16,F"We defeated the parties of
OL,17,Fbillionaire donors because this is
OL,18,FManchester. We do things differently
OL,19,Fhere."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
